$ HTML tag: label

A `<label>` is connected to an → development/web/HTML/tags/input[`<input>`] via its *for* attribute. Mouse clicking on the label «activates» the connected input-field.

There is also a *title* attribute that becomes active when the mouse hovers over the label.

